INSERT INTO translation(literal_id, language, is_default, text)  VALUES (@maxId+3, "EN", 1, "The IIRSM, established in 1975, is a professional membership body that provides recognition, information, support and enhancement for health and safety professionals and specialist members related to the health and safety field. It was created to advance professional standards in accident prevention and occupational health throughout the world. Over the last three decades, the IIRSM has grown from a collective group of UK health and safety professionals to a thriving international institute covering over 70 countries. Its main objective is to advance public education in accident prevention and occupational health in industry. To achieve this, the institute promotes research into accident prevention and occupational health and publishes the results, encourages individuals to adopt health and safety best practice and help prevent accidents, advises anyone entering the health and safety field to undertake training and obtain professional qualifications, and exchanges information with equivalent bodies throughout the world.");
